Dialogs.Dialog: Y-You don't have to stare at me！
It's special for you that we get this close.
I'm your girlfriend. This is just normal！
I can be by your side, right...？
Are you transforming into a pervert king again？
No, I wouldn't say that this is bad...
It's written on your face that you want to flirt.
Can you come here a bit？
Ah, it shouldn't be like that...
Hah... You just don't get it...
Hmm？ Do you have some other things on your mind？
Did you get bored of Rinko...？
I can't go on with this... Sorry.
If you're asking me whether I feel it or not, the answer is "No."
Don't get carried away！ Shall I give you a kick？
Can't you think more about Rinko's feelings？
It's not like I'm waiting for this.
Rinko didn't hurt your feelings, right？
Your eyes... If you keep them open, it'll be embarrassing...
Hey, do you want to kiss Rinko？
While we're kissing, you should close your eyes.
Rinko's been thinking about the same thing...
You knew it... Don't tease me.
Why do you want to kiss Rinko this much？
No... not yet. How about a little bit more？
Hey. Do you like to kiss Rinko？
Hey... Why are you... so good at kissing？
Somehow, I started to like kissing more and more. ...Am I a bad girl？
If I say that I want you to kiss me, will you hate me？
No, I can't let you stop now.
It's bad if you stop now.
What to do？ How about some more？
Too bad. It's still not enough.
Rinko and her boyfriend are so lovey-dovey. Are you jealous？
We are the most lovey-dovey couple in the world！
Rinko wants to be with you like this forever...
This kiss... Rinko will never ever forget it.
So crafty... How did you make Rinko love you so much like this？
Forever... And ever... Never leave Rinko, okay？
...Can you say that you love me？
Today is special... I love you.
Please... Say that you love Rinko.
You're so handsome today. Maybe it's just Rinko's imagination though...
You must be with Rinko a little longer！ Rinko is so selfish after all.
Keep this as a secret between us, okay？
Can you tell me how much you love me...？
I feel calm when I'm with you... Except for when we kiss, though...
I wonder if other couples also kiss like we just did...
Do we kiss too much...？ It can't be helped when my boyfriend is indecent...
How many times have we kissed？ It's uncountable already, right？
Am I addicted to kissing already？ An indecent girl isn't good, right？
Rinko really loves kissing. Only with you, okay？
Why is it？ No matter how many times we kiss, it's never enough...
You look like a pervert. This is it for today.
When we kiss, Rinko becomes frank. Is it bad？！？
Are you nervous？ You shouldn't. I'll also try not to be nervous.
Our faces must look very funny when we kiss, right？
Hey！ Take a look at your face in the mirror！ You're grinning... Pervert！
Sorry... Rinko needs you more and more...
Ah... I got attacked by this mysterious kisser again today... Not that I hate it though.
Rinko is extremely happy now. Do you know that？
Today, I'm Rinko the cat. Spoil me and I'll cry "meow, meow." Hehe...
Why is it only Rinko who feels like a fool！？
I see. So you don't like to do this with Rinko！
Let's wait until later... Can you be patient？
Rinko isn't in the mood for this right now...
Hey, if you aren't gonna kiss...
Why did it turn out like this？ ...Geez！
This time... It isn't comparable to the last time.
If this is what you like... If it is, Rinko won't say a thing about it...
If this isn't enough for you to understand what I'm thinking, maybe we should kiss some more.
Do people get used to kissing when they do it often？ I've been kissed so many times that I start to like it.
Hey？ Why do you kiss Rinko？ Because you love Rinko... right？
All we've done was kiss and kiss. Now, you've turned Rinko into a pervert like you.
Rather than a smooch, can you try to kiss Rinko in a more mature way？
If the teacher knew that we kiss so often like this, will we get scolded？ I'm not afraid though.
Who made Rinko become like this...？ That person will have to take responsibility！
No matter how many times we kiss, my heart won't stop throbbing.
Rinko is cheeky and not cute, but she still wants to hear you say that she is dear to you...
We kissed a lot... Hehe... But it's still not enough.
You will always love Rinko, right？
Hey, one question. Do you know why Rinko feels this happy...？
It annoys me that now I feel like I'm the happiest person in the world.
Please don't worry... They're just tears of happiness...
Why do I cry when I feel happy...？ Whose fault is it？ ...You idiot.
You're the person I love most in the world... I'll never lose you...
I've confessed to you, so will you be the one to propose first...？ Am I too selfish？
You like it, right？ Hey, hey.
I'm still not used to this...
You do like it, don't you？ Hehe.
You like it, don't you？ Haha.
You like this kind of thing...
